<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 04:09:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列最高法院即使没有组建新政府，也可能为新的正统派犹太人铺平道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-may-have-paved-the-way-for-the-new-haredi-jew-if-not-a-new-government/00000190-5141-de50-af9b-7fed1c6c0000</link><description>高等法院强制征召犹太学生的裁决不会让内塔尼亚胡的联盟垮台，因为他和他的极端正统派伙伴只是想避免不可避免的事情</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 03:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-may-have-paved-the-way-for-the-new-haredi-jew-if-not-a-new-government/00000190-5141-de50-af9b-7fed1c6c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列负担沉重的公众感到沮丧。它不会让军方通过象征性的正统征兵而逃脱惩罚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-frustrated-public-wont-let-the-military-get-away-with-a-symbolic-haredi-draft/00000190-50e3-de50-af9b-7fef8e770000</link><description>加沙正在进行的战争凸显了以色列国防军服役人员与国家豁免人员之间的不平等有多么严重。法院的裁决为新的服役模式和替代的国民服役形式创造了机会。如果参谋长联手回避这个问题，一波愤怒可能会危及“人民军队”模式</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 03:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-frustrated-public-wont-let-the-military-get-away-with-a-symbolic-haredi-draft/00000190-50e3-de50-af9b-7fef8e770000</guid></item><item><title>美国：与真主党的战争将是“灾难性的”； Gallant：以色列更倾向于外交解决方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article-live/u-s-war-with-hezbollah-would-be-catastrophic-gallant-israel-prefers-diplomacy/00000190-524c-d37f-a392-7aee8aa30000</link><description>报告：美国官员警告真主党不要认为自己能够阻止以色列袭击黎巴嫩 ■ 奥斯汀表示，美国迫切寻求以色列与真主党之间达成外交协议 ■ 加兰特告诉奥斯汀，阻止伊朗发展核武器的“时间已经不多了” ■ 内塔尼亚胡：“致力于”拜登概述的以色列提议 美国军事参谋长表示，美国可能无法像对付伊朗那样保护以色列免受真主党的袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 02:17:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article-live/u-s-war-with-hezbollah-would-be-catastrophic-gallant-israel-prefers-diplomacy/00000190-524c-d37f-a392-7aee8aa30000</guid></item><item><title>联盟高级消息人士担心，如果以色列军队征兵法未能在七月最后期限前通过，政府就不会垮台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/senior-coalition-sources-fear-collapse-if-conscription-law-doesnt-pass-by-july-deadline/00000190-5069-de50-af9b-7fed94820000</link><description>虽然内塔尼亚胡政府相信联盟将能够经受住周二高等法院反对极端正统军队豁免的裁决的风暴，但他们担心，如果他们提议的征兵法没有在议会获得通过，联盟可能会分崩离析</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:39:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/senior-coalition-sources-fear-collapse-if-conscription-law-doesnt-pass-by-july-deadline/00000190-5069-de50-af9b-7fed94820000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院对正统派法律草案的裁决令极端正统派政党陷入混乱，并使内塔尼亚胡的联盟面临风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-ruling-send-ultra-orthodox-parties-scrambling-puts-netanyahu-coalition-at-risk/00000190-507a-d3c0-a5d4-737a0c910000</link><description>以色列最高法院决定命令国家征召正统派人士，并停止向不合作的犹太教派提供资金，这让极端正统派政党陷入了严重的困境。虽然他们不排除解散议会的可能性，但他们明白他们没有真正的政治选择</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:15:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-ruling-send-ultra-orthodox-parties-scrambling-puts-netanyahu-coalition-at-risk/00000190-507a-d3c0-a5d4-737a0c910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长命令国防机构立即招募 3,000 名极端正统派加入以色列国防军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-orders-defense-establishment-to-immediately-recruit-3-000-ultra-orthodox/00000190-5026-d3c0-a5d4-7366941a0000</link><description>以色列高等法院一致裁定极端正统派男子有义务服兵役几个小时后，总检察长加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉致信国防部长和政府，表示国家必须遵守法院的裁决，并立即开始军队服役。流程草案</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 17:07:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-orders-defense-establishment-to-immediately-recruit-3-000-ultra-orthodox/00000190-5026-d3c0-a5d4-7366941a0000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日，特朗普认可了一部有关哈马斯强奸的电影。他只是忘记提及强奸事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-25/ty-article/.highlight/trump-endorsed-a-film-about-hamas-rape-on-october-7-he-just-forgot-to-mention-the-rape/00000190-5018-d91c-abba-ff1844930000</link><description>特朗普在出人意料地呼吁观看有关哈马斯性暴力的纪录片《沉默前的尖叫》时表示，该纪录片“生动地描绘了哈马斯所造成的死亡和破坏。”这把他的主张变成了一种否认</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 16:52:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-25/ty-article/.highlight/trump-endorsed-a-film-about-hamas-rape-on-october-7-he-just-forgot-to-mention-the-rape/00000190-5018-d91c-abba-ff1844930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 263 天：联合国停止在加沙的援助行动，直到工人得到更好的保护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-263-un-to-halt-aid-ops-in-gaza-until-workers-are-better-protected/00000190-5019-d8cb-a19d-595b23550000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡高级助手表示不可能让哈马斯消失 ■ 哈马斯政治局主席伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚的妹妹在以色列对加沙城的袭击中丧生 ■ 据报道，巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯将访问俄罗斯 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡的妻子告诉人质的家人，她认为以色列国防军领导人想要上演反对她丈夫的政变 ■ 战争进入 263 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 16:23:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-263-un-to-halt-aid-ops-in-gaza-until-workers-are-better-protected/00000190-5019-d8cb-a19d-595b23550000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦权力机构内部的权力斗争正好影响了以色列削弱巴勒斯坦权力机构的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/power-struggles-within-palestinian-authority-play-into-israels-plans-of-weakening-it/00000190-4dfb-d8cb-a19d-4dfb722f0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦振兴巴解组织的倡议遭到巴勒斯坦权力机构的严厉批评。这些内部斗争影响了以色列控制加沙地带、加强对约旦河西岸的控制以及导致巴勒斯坦唯一代表机构崩溃的计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:14:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/power-struggles-within-palestinian-authority-play-into-israels-plans-of-weakening-it/00000190-4dfb-d8cb-a19d-4dfb722f0000</guid></item><item><title>“时间不多了”：加兰特敦促美国与以色列合作应对伊朗威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/gallant-to-blinken-eyes-of-enemies-on-u-s-israel-ties-dispute-must-be-solved-quickly/00000190-4fb2-d91c-abba-efb228cc0000</link><description>在访问华盛顿期间，以色列国防部长告诉美国国防部长帮助以色列应对伊朗核计划迫在眉睫的威胁。加兰特还告诉布林肯，“我们敌人的眼睛”关注着以色列与美国的紧张局势，并表示他们的争端必须迅速解决</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:08:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/gallant-to-blinken-eyes-of-enemies-on-u-s-israel-ties-dispute-must-be-solved-quickly/00000190-4fb2-d91c-abba-efb228cc0000</guid></item><item><title>守门员和维和人员：以色列基布兹尼克、贝都因人和撤离人员团结起来踢足球</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/goal-and-peace-keepers-israeli-kibbutzniks-bedouin-and-evacuees-unite-for-soccer-tourney/00000190-4ec8-d91c-abba-efd8a5d80000</link><description>为了保持传统和理智，米什马尔哈埃梅克基布兹 (Kibbutz Mishmar HaEmek) 的居民、卡阿比耶村 (Ka&amp;#39;abiyye) 和纳哈尔奥兹 (Nahal Oz) 的撤离人员联合起来参加足球比赛。每个人都是赢家</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 14:38:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/goal-and-peace-keepers-israeli-kibbutzniks-bedouin-and-evacuees-unite-for-soccer-tourney/00000190-4ec8-d91c-abba-efd8a5d80000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩政界人士、专家和民众担心以色列和真主党之间爆发全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/fearing-israel-hezbollah-all-out-war-lebanese-politicians-pundits-and-people-speak-out/00000190-4f4a-d8cb-a19d-4f4b8e660000</link><description>随着#LebanonDoesNotWantAWar 标签在社交媒体上流行，黎巴嫩主要政客寻求缓和局势，神职人员谴责“犹太复国主义干涉”，黎巴嫩公民公开批评真主党</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 14:19:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/fearing-israel-hezbollah-all-out-war-lebanese-politicians-pundits-and-people-speak-out/00000190-4f4a-d8cb-a19d-4f4b8e660000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的高级顾问表示“哈马斯是一个想法”，无法用武力击败，加沙需要替代方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/pms-top-adviser-hamas-is-an-idea-that-cant-be-beaten-by-force-gaza-needs-alternative/00000190-4f8c-d3c0-a5d4-6fee02190000</link><description>以色列国家安全负责人查奇·哈内比周一在安全会议上表示，以色列需要提出替代哈马斯在加沙统治的方案，“而不仅仅是摧毁其军事能力”。上周，以色列国防军发言人也说了同样的话，很快遭到总理批评</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 14:19:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/pms-top-adviser-hamas-is-an-idea-that-cant-be-beaten-by-force-gaza-needs-alternative/00000190-4f8c-d3c0-a5d4-6fee02190000</guid></item><item><title>总理的妻子萨拉·内塔尼亚胡告诉人质家属，军队首长希望发动政变反对她的丈夫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wife-tells-hostage-families-idf-chiefs-want-to-stage-coup-against-her-husband/00000190-4f8c-d8cb-a19d-4fcf448c0000</link><description>在与少数人质家庭的一次小型会议上，总理的妻子一再表示她不信任军队领导人。代表内塔尼亚胡夫人的发言人表示，有关内塔尼亚胡夫人的虚假、有倾向性和持续的泄密行为构成了令人发指的不公正行为。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 13:55:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wife-tells-hostage-families-idf-chiefs-want-to-stage-coup-against-her-husband/00000190-4f8c-d8cb-a19d-4fcf448c0000</guid></item><item><title>由于与真主党的紧张关系加剧，加拿大延长了以色列人的工作签证期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/canada-extends-work-visa-deadline-for-israelis-due-to-rising-tensions-with-hezbollah/00000190-4f45-d3c0-a5d4-6f67eafd0000</link><description>以色列-哈马斯战争爆发后，加拿大最初于二月份向以色列人开放了签证计划，并提供三年期工作许可证，对职业或教育没有限制。截止日期原定于 6 月截止，但现已延长至 2025 年 7 月底</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 13:34:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/canada-extends-work-visa-deadline-for-israelis-due-to-rising-tensions-with-hezbollah/00000190-4f45-d3c0-a5d4-6f67eafd0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日以色列袭击事件受害者起诉近东救济工程处，指控其为哈马斯洗钱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/victims-of-oct-7-attack-against-israel-sue-unrwa-for-allegedly-laundering-money-for-hamas/00000190-4f5e-d768-adf8-4ffead600000</link><description>10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀的数十名受害者在一项诉讼中指控，近东救济工程处向哈马斯工作人员支付工资，并通过学校传播哈马斯的宣传，以此协助哈马斯。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 13:24:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/victims-of-oct-7-attack-against-israel-sue-unrwa-for-allegedly-laundering-money-for-hamas/00000190-4f5e-d768-adf8-4ffead600000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示内塔尼亚胡的联盟受欢迎程度继续下降，斯莫特里奇退出议会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/poll-shows-netanyahus-coalition-continues-to-lose-popularity-smotrich-out-of-knesset/00000190-4e2b-da42-a1ba-7f6b8dd60000</link><description>Channel 12 的一项民意调查显示，在内塔尼亚胡的联盟党派中，阿耶·德里领导的沙斯党赢得了 10 个席位，联合托拉犹太教赢得了 8 个席位。虽然伊塔马尔·本·格维尔（Itamar Ben-Gvir）的政党获得了九个席位，但贝扎莱·斯莫特里奇（Bezalel Smotrich）的宗教犹太复国主义并未通过选举门槛</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 12:49:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/poll-shows-netanyahus-coalition-continues-to-lose-popularity-smotrich-out-of-knesset/00000190-4e2b-da42-a1ba-7f6b8dd60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院法官恢复探视监狱，但不会探视关押巴勒斯坦人的监狱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-top-court-justices-resume-prison-visits-but-wont-see-those-holding-palestinians/00000190-4f14-da42-a1ba-7f7e97800000</link><description>最高法院法官有权对所有监狱进行随机和预先安排的访问，以评估囚犯的关押条件。自加沙战争爆发以来，没有对关押巴勒斯坦囚犯的设施进行过此类参观</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 12:47:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-top-court-justices-resume-prison-visits-but-wont-see-those-holding-palestinians/00000190-4f14-da42-a1ba-7f7e97800000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院“想要发动宗教战争”：正统MKs抨击对极端正统选秀的戏剧性裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-wants-to-force-religious-war-haredi-mks-blast-ruling-on-ultra-orthodox-draft/00000190-4ee9-d91c-abba-eff97d690000</link><description>高等法院一致裁决要求国家起草正统律法，引起了各个政治派别的强烈反应，一位政治家表示，“世界上没有任何力量可以阻止以色列人民学习托拉”，其他人则称该法院是“从民选政府手中夺取权力的独裁机构”</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 11:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-wants-to-force-religious-war-haredi-mks-blast-ruling-on-ultra-orthodox-draft/00000190-4ee9-d91c-abba-eff97d690000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人和阿拉伯人是这座以色列城市的好邻居。然后定居者带着枪出现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jews-and-arabs-were-good-neighbors-in-this-city-then-settlers-showed-up-with-guns/00000190-4e8e-da42-a1ba-7fee2d330000</link><description>拜特谢安市的阿拉伯社区主要由与以色列安全部队合作的家庭组成。暴力右翼极端分子决定他们不能留在那里</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 11:04:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jews-and-arabs-were-good-neighbors-in-this-city-then-settlers-showed-up-with-guns/00000190-4e8e-da42-a1ba-7fee2d330000</guid></item></channel></rss>